/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:7:The chain is at its best when it refuses cosmetic exact-rewrite optimism. It is weakest where it assumes that "destroyed by Tao averaging" can be operationalized into a usable screening rule without importing substantial additional technical structure.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:15:- "State exactly what Tao's averaged equations preserve" is not yet a concrete task unless the chain names the comparison granularity. Preserve at what level: identities, coercive estimates, local energy inequalities, geometric transport, concentration scenarios, or blowup mechanisms? Without that, the preserved/destroyed ledger will be partly semantic.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:26:- The example list already nudges the search toward currently fashionable exact-NS markers: pressure Hessian, alignment, circulation/topology, stochastic flow. That is not neutral curation; it preloads the outcome with mechanisms already easy to narrate in Tao-filter language.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:28:- "One-line Tao verdicts" and "one-line novelty notes" are too compressed for the burden being placed on them. A one-line verdict is exactly how a subtle but ambiguous candidate gets prematurely labeled "identity-level" and buried.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:50:- "Supposed gain is only cosmetic" is again a vulnerable phrase. Cosmetic relative to what closure scheme? A gain that is cosmetic for De Giorgi may be decisive for concentration-compactness or Lagrangian persistence. Because the chain spans multiple architectures, the anti-cosmetic test needs architecture-specific criteria, not one global slogan.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:68:### 1. The chain confuses Tao-discrimination with proof relevance
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:70:The mission filter is necessary, but this chain treats it as almost sufficient for early-stage ranking. That is not warranted. Many features are genuinely absent from the averaged model and still mathematically useless for regularity. The chain knows this in words, but its workflow still gives Tao-discrimination too much agenda-setting power.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:94:- It correctly treats Tao's averaged-model obstruction as a hard filter rather than background color.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-01.md:101:If this chain is kept, it should be interpreted primarily as a falsification chain, not a discovery-ranking chain. The honest success condition is not "produce 1-2 promoted discriminators." It is "show, under a strict admissibility and comparability standard, whether any candidate survives contact with a named bottleneck in a way that is stronger than slogan-level Tao discrimination." Without that tightening, the most likely output is a polished ranking memo with weak epistemic content.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:5:- `beta = 4/3` is already sharp for the De Giorgi-Vasseur architecture. This run does not spend budget on new De Giorgi tuning, pressure-`H^1` relabeling, or weakly disguised recursion variants.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:6:- Run-001 closed the harmonic-tail loophole **inside** the far-field coefficient-shrinkage architecture. That negative should be reused, not ignored, but it does not rule out pressure structure in a different tensor or rigidity architecture.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:8:- Run-003 and Step 006 closed the fixed local-energy exact-rewrite audit: divergence, Lamb-vector/projected, and vorticity/Biot-Savart rewrites do not buy a Tao-sensitive gain on the frozen LEI cutoff-flux term.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:9:- The new portfolio therefore pivots away from already-audited local architectures and toward exact NS structure that Tao-style averaging plausibly destroys.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:13:### Chain 01 - Tao Differential Diagnosis And Mechanism Ranking
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:15:Central premise: before committing scarce budget to one mechanism, compare exact NS against Tao's averaged model directly and rank only those discriminators that are both genuinely destroyed by averaging and operational inside a named proof architecture.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:17:Why it belongs now: the mission is explicitly filtered by Tao's 2016 obstruction, and the fastest way to waste budget is to chase attractive but Tao-robust structure. This chain has the strongest failure payload.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:27:Central premise: the exact tensor relations among strain, pressure Hessian, and vorticity stretching may encode NS-specific sign, eigenframe, or local harmonic structure that scalar norm methods erase.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:29:Why it belongs now: it reuses the pressure-side context without reopening the killed coefficient-shrinkage branch, and it sits between geometry and compactness without collapsing into either.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:33:Central premise: exact NS may retain a transport-topological backbone through circulation, helicity, vortex-line organization, or stochastic Lagrangian formulations that Tao-style averaging destroys.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:41:- Chain 03 is tensorial and local. It targets eigenvalues, eigenvectors, and pressure-Hessian structure on the stretching side.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:48:- Best bridge branch: Chain 03. It can connect pressure structure, vorticity stretching, and Tao discrimination without reopening old norm-based pressure routes.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:57:If the next execution wants the best bridge from prior pressure findings to a new architecture, start with Chain 03.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner.md:63:No Lorentz-space or other De Giorgi-iteration variant is carried forward here. The mission context says not to spend budget on further De Giorgi modification, and the portfolio follows that instruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:1:# Chain 01 - Tao Differential Diagnosis And Mechanism Ranking
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:5:The mission is filtered by Tao's averaged-model obstruction, so the first live branch is to compare exact NS against the averaged model directly and promote only those exact structures that are both genuinely destroyed by averaging and concrete enough to drive a later proof architecture.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:16:This chain is not a proof attempt in one fixed architecture. It is a Tao-filtered mechanism audit whose product is a ranked map of the live non-De-Giorgi landscape.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:23:- Action: state exactly what Tao's averaged equations preserve for this mission and what kind of evidence is required to say an NS feature is truly destroyed by averaging.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:31:- Action: shortlist at most four candidate NS-only structures, for example pressure-Hessian tensor algebra, strain-vorticity alignment identities, Lagrangian circulation or topology, or stochastic flow structure.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-01.md:33:- Expected output: a discriminator table with one-line Tao verdicts and one-line novelty notes relative to prior runs.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:7:The problem is that the chain is still mostly a Kenig-Merle style template with the key novelty compressed into an undefined phrase: "an exact NS structure unavailable to Tao's averaged model." Until that phrase is made concrete, the chain is not a research program so much as a hope that one missing NS-only rigidity input exists. The biggest risk is not that the chain is too ambitious; it is that it can generate polished memos while never confronting the actual hard obstruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:14:- `\dot H^{1/2}` has a cleaner Hilbert-space profile technology than `BMO^{-1}`, but it is less naturally tied to the suitable-weak-solution machinery that usually feeds local energy and backward-uniqueness style arguments.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:15:- `BMO^{-1}` is the weakest candidate in this menu for a compactness-rigidity program. It is excellent for small-data mild theory, but it is a poor default host for a large-data minimal blowup extraction unless one can point to a concrete nonlinear profile decomposition and a robust stability theory in exactly that setting.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:17:So the step's framing is too loose. "Rank realistic spaces" sounds harmless, but the real burden is to prove that at least one space supports the whole package: local theory, perturbation theory, profile decomposition, symmetry normalization, pressure control, and a notion of compactness compatible with the intended rigidity lever. A ranking memo can hide the fact that no candidate actually clears that bar.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:25:- The proposed levers are placeholders, not mechanisms. "Tensor-sign law," "Lagrangian/topological invariant," and "pressure-Hessian feature" are categories, not usable objects.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:26:- The filter "reject anything Tao's averaged model plausibly preserves" is not a reliable research criterion. A lever can fail in the averaged model for irrelevant reasons, or survive averaging and still be exactly the right tool for real NS.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:27:- Requiring Tao-sensitivity before the extraction package is built biases the search toward novelty theater. It rewards mechanisms that sound NS-specific rather than mechanisms that can actually be applied to an almost-periodic critical element.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:29:There is also a sequencing problem. In most compactness-rigidity programs, the hypothetical critical element tells you what rigidity information is even geometrically available. Here the chain asks for the rigidity weapon before it knows the target's regularity, compactness modulus, or pressure information. That is backwards.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:31:The kill condition is too aggressive in one direction and too permissive in another. It is too aggressive because a promising route might only reveal the right rigidity quantity after the minimal object is formulated. It is too permissive because merely "naming" a Tao-sensitive lever is not progress unless one can state its sign, monotonicity, coercivity, or contradiction mechanism on the intended class of solutions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:39:- Symmetry normalization is not trivial. Spatial translation and scaling are obvious, but Galilean issues, pressure normalization, and the chosen solution framework all affect what "minimal" even means.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:43:The kill condition again sounds precise but is softer than it looks. A "clean formulation" can be written on paper while still relying on unproved profile decomposition, unproved critical stability, or an incompatible solution class. The step should fail unless the object is definable with a clear dependency graph to known results and one sharply identified missing theorem.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:51:- The pressure term is a recurring spoiler. Any rigidity mechanism that depends on second-order pressure structure can fail simply because the available compactness is too weak to pass that structure to the limit.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:55:The downgrade rule is also too binary. A lever can fail without collapsing to Tao-preserved structure. It can fail because the compactness class is too weak, because the quantity is not coercive, or because the limiting object lacks the regularity needed to state the argument. Those are different failure modes and should be separated.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:69:- The whole chain is structurally biased toward a predetermined conclusion: if local estimates stall, pivot to concentration-compactness plus rigidity. That is a familiar aesthetic move, not an argued reason that this is the best remaining path.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:71:- The Tao-averaged-model filter is doing too much conceptual work. "Unavailable to Tao's averaged model" is not itself evidence of relevance, tractability, or sharpness.
