/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-03.md:94:- strain-eigenvalue and vorticity-alignment criteria;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-03.md:96:- pressure-Hessian closure heuristics and restricted-Euler style reductions;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-03.md:136:The fair verdict is that this chain should be run mainly as a negative-discovery program. If it succeeds, the success standard has to be very high: not a prettier tensor identity, not a reduced eigenframe toy model, and not another alignment-flavored criterion, but a mechanism that survives full nonlocal coupling and clearly breaks beyond what Tao-style averaging preserves. Anything short of that is obstruction mapping, not a live route.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-04.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-04.md:5:The exact NS equations may retain a transport-topological backbone, through circulation, helicity, vortex-line organization, or stochastic Lagrangian flow structure, that Tao-style averaging destroys. If regularity depends on that backbone, neutral Eulerian geometry screens were looking in the wrong place.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-04.md:16:This chain is organized around transport and topology rather than around Eulerian local estimates, tensor eigenframes, or concentration-compactness.
