/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-04.md:28:### Step 2 - State the exact Tao discriminator
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-04.md:33:- Expected output: a Tao-screen memo for the promoted object.
