/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-02.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-02.md:5:If all local estimate cleanups are exhausted, the remaining path may be to assume blowup, extract a minimal counterexample in a critical phase space, and rule it out using a rigidity mechanism that depends on exact NS structure unavailable to Tao's averaged model.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-02.md:16:This is the only chain that starts from a hypothetical singular solution and tries to win globally through concentration-compactness and rigidity rather than through a new local estimate.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/selected/chain-02.md:30:- Action: choose one exact NS structure that could exclude the critical element, such as a tensor-sign law, Lagrangian/topological invariant, or a pressure-Hessian feature.
