/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-01.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-01.md:5:The mission is filtered by Tao's averaged-model obstruction, so the first live branch is to compare exact NS against the averaged model directly and promote only those exact structures that are both genuinely destroyed by averaging and concrete enough to drive a later proof architecture.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-01.md:16:This chain is not a proof attempt in one fixed architecture. It is a Tao-filtered mechanism audit whose product is a ranked map of the live non-De-Giorgi landscape.
