/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-03.md:76:- front-load the Tao filter
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-03.md:88:- The probability of a genuinely new positive bridge from local Beltrami geometry to a usable regularity criterion looks low.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-03.md:89:- The probability of a presentable negative result is materially higher, because the attack has isolated a concrete obstruction: local near-Beltrami structure may only control a local/self-induced part of stretching while leaving the scale-critical nonlocal remainder untouched.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:7:The strongest repair is not to discard the chain. It is to flip its default posture. This branch should be run as an obstruction-first helical-symbol program whose positive branch survives only if one exact feature can be written as an explicit candidate inequality and still wins after dyadic summation, mixed-helicity restoration, and any needed localization.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:21:The attacker is right that a ledger of helicity signs, resonance classes, and Leray-symbol identities is cheap unless it is tied to the sign, size, or summability of a specific term in a specific estimate. The original chain also left "Tao-sensitive" too informal. The refined chain keeps the ledger but makes it operational: each promoted feature must be attached to the chosen estimate and assigned a maximal plausible quantitative effect before full reconstruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:23:### 3. The distinction between exact NS structure and Tao-style averaging was not defined sharply enough
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:33:This lands cleanly. Once a mechanism is promoted, the chain should already be able to write the candidate inequality, transfer estimate, or contradiction line where the mechanism enters. Otherwise the route has not crossed from interpretation to proof pressure. The refined chain now requires an explicit candidate inequality in Step 3.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:45:Correct. In this subject the best-looking same-helicity or near-resonant sectors are often exactly where full-equation relevance is weakest. The refined chain therefore requires any restricted interaction class to come with a quantified share of the relevant transfer or shell sum. Otherwise the branch dies as a regime artifact.
