/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/judgments/chain-02.md:31:### 2. Step 2 uses placeholder rigidity ideas and overweights Tao-sensitivity
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/judgments/chain-02.md:35:The original levers were categories, not mechanisms. Also, "unavailable to Tao's averaged model" is too weak to serve as a hard admission criterion. It can still be used as a secondary filter, but only after a candidate quantity is shown to be defined on the actual compactness class and to offer a concrete contradiction mechanism.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/judgments/chain-02.md:41:This sequencing objection is correct. The hypothetical critical element determines what regularity, compactness, pressure control, and normalization are actually available. Those facts should discipline rigidity selection. The refined chain therefore moves critical-object formulation ahead of final rigidity promotion.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/judgments/chain-02.md:85:3. It screens rigidity quantities only on the actual critical-element class, with Tao-sensitivity demoted to a secondary filter.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:5:This chain is better disciplined than a generic "look at alignment" program, but it still leans too hard on a hope that one well-chosen tensor observable will retain NS-specific content after the pressure nonlocality is charged honestly. That hope is exactly where many prior routes have already died. The chain sees some of those hazards, but mostly treats them as screening criteria rather than as reasons the whole strategy may be structurally low-yield.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:7:The strongest feature is that it explicitly forces confrontation with pressure debt, eigenvalue degeneracy, and negative outcomes. The weakest feature is that the core discriminator is not operational: "survives Tao sensitivity and controls full stretching" sounds selective, but in practice it may just restate the original difficulty in more refined language.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:17:- The local-plus-harmonic pressure split does not neutralize the hard part. The harmful freedom is precisely that the pressure Hessian is nonlocal and can re-enter with the same scaling as the stretching term. Bookkeeping the debt is not close to paying it.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:26:- The candidate list is already crowded with near-prior-art objects: eigenvalue gaps, vorticity-eigenframe alignment, and pressure/strain misalignment are all obvious descendants of the standard alignment literature. Renaming or slightly repackaging them will not make them structurally new.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:28:- The admissibility rules are too qualitative. "Concrete role," "dynamic meaning," and "explicit Tao discriminator" sound strict, but without a quantitative threshold they leave room to keep whichever observable feels narratively attractive.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:34:### Step 3 - Stress-test Tao sensitivity and eigenframe stability before estimates
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:36:The intent is good, but the Tao screen is underdefined and risks becoming a cargo-cult anti-toy-model check.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:38:- The chain assumes there is a clear statement of what should fail in Tao's averaged setting for a meaningful NS observable. Usually there is not. Many quantities fail in a toy model for accidental reasons, and many quantities survive for reasons unrelated to the real PDE mechanism.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:50:- Charging all nonlocal pressure-Hessian debt explicitly is again correct, but the likely outcome is that the debt is of the same order and complexity as the asset. The chain seems to know this, yet still acts as if a well-designed observable might survive. That is the central hidden assumption and it is very strong.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:51:- The "harmonic far-field contribution" language is a reminder of the real issue, but it also shows how badly local tensor geometry is outmatched. Far-field effects can alter the pressure Hessian without respecting the local alignment picture the chain is trying to exploit.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:62:- A proposition-scale target can itself be misleading. A cleanly stated conditional lemma may look like progress even when the hypothesis is effectively equivalent to controlling the dangerous part of the pressure Hessian, which is the original problem translated into a better sentence.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:71:The chain is framed as a funnel for finding the right tensor observable. But the deeper possibility is not that the current observables are poorly chosen; it is that any low-dimensional observable of local tensor geometry is too compressed to dominate a nonlocal pressure-coupled mechanism. The chain treats this as a possible outcome, but still organizes itself around the search for a survivor.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:75:Terms like "Tao discriminator," "full stretching," and "nonlocal debt" sound like strong safeguards. In reality they do not bite until one tries to prove an estimate. Before that, they mainly discipline language. That means the chain can look selective while remaining permissive in practice.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:79:This route lives adjacent to a large literature on vortex stretching, eigenvalue alignment, pressure Hessian geometry, and conditional regularity criteria. Putting the literature benchmark in Step 5 invites redundancy. A serious prior-art check should happen before Step 2 narrows candidates, not after a candidate is emotionally invested.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:83:Most kill conditions rely on judgments like "no one-sided leverage target," "post hoc Tao discriminator," or "outside genuine new leverage." Those are sensible phrases, but they leave enough discretion to keep the chain alive through ambiguous evidence. The danger is not excessive harshness; it is slow failure by interpretive generosity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:91:- The chain does not hide from the pressure Hessian. That is a real strength and better than routes that quietly replace full stretching by a local caricature.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:98:As an honesty filter on tensor-observable ideas, this chain is good. As a likely generator of genuinely new leverage on 3D NS regularity, it is weak-to-moderate at best. The central reason is structural: the route is still betting that local tensor geometry can be distilled into an observable that survives nonlocal pressure coupling with enough coercive force to matter. That is precisely the kind of compression that prior work has repeatedly failed to make decisive.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/attacks/chain-03.md:100:The most likely successful output is not a new criterion but a sharp obstruction memo explaining why tensor-level alignment information remains informative yet non-coercive once the full pressure debt is charged. That is a respectable result, but it means the chain is better understood as a falsification program for this research instinct than as a serious positive route past De Giorgi.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-02.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-02.md:5:If the true Navier-Stokes equations possess a structural property that Tao-style averaging destroys, the cleanest place to look is the exact Leray-projected quadratic symbol and its helical-triad interaction geometry. The branch is live only if one triad-level feature yields a concrete gain on one named bottleneck quantity after all summation and localization costs are charged.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-02.md:32:- Action: decompose the NS nonlinearity into the chosen triad variables and record which sign, helicity, or resonance constraints are exact and which are only bookkeeping.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-02.md:33:- Action: identify which parts depend on the exact Leray symbol and which parts a Tao-style averaged model could preserve at the same comparison level.
