/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-02.md:51:- Action: test whether the claimed gain survives perturbation away from exactly favorable helicity or resonance classes.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-03.md:3:## Central Premise
