/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/refined/chain-02.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/refined/chain-02.md:5:Exact helical-triad geometry is worth pursuing only against one fixed theorem-level bottleneck and under a presumption of obstruction. The branch is live only if one exact Leray-symbol feature can be written as an explicit gain in one named estimate or contradiction step and still survive dyadic summation, mixed-helicity restoration, and any required localization.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/refined/chain-02.md:12:- a sharp obstruction memo stating exactly where helical-symbol structure dies: endpoint mismatch, effect-size insufficiency, shell or angular summation collapse, mixed-helicity collapse, localization collapse, or regime-only irrelevance.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/refined/chain-02.md:16:This chain stays at the exact Fourier-symbol level, but it no longer treats elegant triad structure as evidence by itself. It is designed mainly to determine whether any Tao-sensitive helical feature produces theorem-grade leverage after honest reconstruction of the full Navier-Stokes interaction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/refined/chain-02.md:33:- Action: decompose the exact Navier-Stokes nonlinearity into the chosen helical-triad variables and record which sign, helicity, resonance, and Leray-projector features are exact.
