/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-03.md:41:- Action: for each shortlisted observable, state exactly what should fail in Tao's averaged model: sign coupling, frame coherence, cancellation, or another named mechanism.
