/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-04.md:39:- Kill condition: if every available rigidity route reduces to Tao-preserved structure, stop and write that as the core obstruction.
