/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:45:- Expected output: a final memo with either a geometry-first attack path or a negative result showing that local Beltrami geometry is too fragile or too non-distinguishing.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:46:- Kill condition: if the same criterion can hold verbatim for the averaged model, close the chain as Tao-blocked.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:7:Its best feature is discipline: it insists on estimate-level gains, it front-loads a Tao screen, and it tries to kill cosmetic rewrites quickly. That is real strength.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:19:### 2. The Tao screen is directionally right but operationally under-specified
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:21:The standard "depends on algebraic structure destroyed by Tao's averaged model" is correct. But the chain uses the weaker proxy "not obviously preserved by Tao's averaged model." That is not enough. Many rewrites can look NS-specific at the identity level and still wash out once one tracks localization, projection, averaging, or frequency interactions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:30:The chain is built around reformulations: Lamb-vector, projected, vorticity, tensor/trilinear rewrites. That is a narrow slice of the space of NS-specific structure. It sidelines mechanisms that are not just rewrites of the same quadratic term, especially dynamic or geometric ones where the useful structure is produced by the flow rather than visible in a static identity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:38:- positive result: must survive Tao, survive localization, survive robustness, and change closure;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:45:The mission context already records that the vorticity formulation also hits the same `beta = 4/3` barrier, and that Beltrami cancellation is extremely fragile. That does not make this chain pointless, but it does mean parts of Step 2 and Step 3 are at risk of spending budget re-certifying known negatives rather than testing genuinely live candidates.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:49:### Step 1 - Fix the target interaction and front-load the Tao screen
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:55:- The chain never commits to which inherited architecture supplies the "target interaction." Is it the De Giorgi truncation bottleneck, a local-energy flux term, a projected pressure term, or something else? Those are not interchangeable. A candidate that helps one may be irrelevant to another.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:58:- The Tao filter is being applied before the chain has specified how the candidate enters a localized estimate. For many structures, the real question is not whether the bare identity survives averaging, but whether the exact interaction between identity, localization, and projection does.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:81:- The chain waits until after a candidate "appears to improve the estimate" before asking whether the effect is just alignment. That is backwards for this mission. Given what is already known about Beltrami fragility, geometry should be built into the first evaluation, not added as a later purity test.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:84:- The step uses near-Beltrami mainly as a fragility screen. That is fair as a guardrail, but it ignores the possibility that localized high-vorticity regions are exactly where one should expect any non-averaged NS structure to manifest.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:90:This is the right pressure test for a surviving signal, but it is too underspecified to protect against pseudo-progress.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:108:- The positive endpoint still uses the standard "why Tao does not immediately erase it" language, which is weaker than what is needed. The chain should require an explicit statement of which feature of the exact NS interaction fails in the averaged model and where that failure enters the estimate.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:5:- `beta = 4/3` is already sharp for the De Giorgi-Vasseur route. This portfolio does not spend budget on more strong-type pressure refinements, H^1/BMO relabeling, or other near-variants of the exhausted chain.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:6:- The prior `vasseur-pressure` mission established that local pressure closes and far-field pressure is the sole obstruction. That result is treated as fixed.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:7:- Tao's 2016 averaged-NS obstruction is the hard filter. Every chain includes an explicit step asking whether the candidate mechanism uses a property of actual Navier-Stokes that averaging destroys.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:20:Central premise: SQG wins by reformulating the drift coupling, not by beating the De Giorgi exponent. This chain asks whether an NS reformulation around the Lamb vector, vorticity transport, or Helmholtz projection exposes a first-order cancellation that the usual velocity-pressure form hides.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:24:### Chain 03 - Geometric Vorticity Alignment and Local Beltrami Tubes
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:26:Central premise: Tao averaging keeps harmonic analysis but destroys fine vortex geometry. Exact Beltrami annihilates the Lamb vector, so the natural question is whether local near-Beltrami structure on intense-vorticity regions can be linked to Constantin-Fefferman style control.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:32:Central premise: if blowup exists, the right object may be a minimal blowup profile, not a sharper local estimate. This chain asks whether the existing NS profile-decomposition machinery is strong enough to isolate a critical element and whether any NS-specific rigidity mechanism survives Tao's filter.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:38:Central premise: the exact tensor identities linking strain, pressure Hessian, and vorticity stretching may contain NS-specific rigidity that averaged quadratic models do not retain. The target is a conditional criterion or obstruction phrased in eigenframe dynamics rather than scalar norms.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:44:- Chain 01 is local and analytic. It exploits harmonicity of the far-field pressure and the local/global mismatch exposed by the previous mission.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:46:- Chain 03 is geometric. It works on coherent structures, alignment, and high-vorticity sets rather than on norms or decompositions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:48:- Chain 05 is tensorial. It focuses on pointwise identities, eigenframes, and strain-pressure coupling rather than tube geometry or compactness.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:54:- Best bridge chain: Chain 05. It can connect the Tao filter, vorticity geometry, and pressure structure without collapsing back into De Giorgi.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:5:The prior mission killed every global H^1-based pressure route because the bad far-field term stayed `O(E_0)`. But `p_far` is harmonic on the local cylinder. This chain tests whether a truly local harmonic norm, annular-energy quantity, or Harnack-decay estimate gives a usable gain outside the De Giorgi framework.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:12:- a sharp obstruction note proving that harmonicity does not generate any Tao-relevant gain.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:16:This is the only chain centered on the local/global mismatch of the far-field pressure term. It does not search for a better De Giorgi exponent and does not revisit the failed global H^1 program.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:23:- Action: rebuild the near/far pressure split from `vasseur-pressure`, isolate the exact place where the far-field term enters with a fixed constant, and record which quantities are already `U_k`-dependent.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:41:### Step 4 - Apply the Tao filter and close the chain
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:44:- Action: compare the surviving mechanism with Tao's averaged NS model and decide whether the argument uses exact NS pressure structure or only generic elliptic harmonicity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:7:Its real strength is discipline. It insists on estimate-level gains, not prettier identities, and it tries to front-load the Tao constraint. That is exactly the right instinct.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:25:### 3. The Tao screen is conceptually right but operationally weak
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:27:The mission context is stronger than "the candidate uses an exact NS-looking feature." Tao's result blocks anything resting only on energy identity plus standard harmonic analysis. So the chain should demand a concrete statement of what the averaged model destroys and where that destruction enters the estimate. As written, a candidate can survive Step 1 by sounding algebraically special without showing that the specialness survives localization and actually matters quantitatively.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:31:Step 3 is built to strip away gains that are "really" geometric or pressure-tensor effects. That is good if the goal is a pure reformulation result. It is bad if the only real NS-specific cancellations are hybrid: exact algebraic form plus alignment, or rewrite plus concentrated tube geometry, or rewrite plus tensor structure. The chain risks discarding the only live mechanisms because they are not pure enough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:35:To promote a positive route, the chain demands a localized gain, Tao relevance, robustness away from special regimes, and a changed closure mechanism. To reach a negative endpoint, it only needs a small shortlist of natural rewrites to collapse back to familiar structure.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:41:The mission context already says the vorticity formulation also lands at the same `beta = 4/3` barrier, and that exact Beltrami cancellation evaporates under tiny perturbation. So some of the most natural Step 2 and Step 3 outputs are already strongly prefigured. The chain is at real risk of spending budget restating known negatives unless it says exactly what new localized estimate is being tested that prior work did not already rule out.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:51:- It never says which bottleneck is mission-central. Is it the De Giorgi truncated pressure contribution, a local-energy flux term, a vorticity stretching localization, or some projected interaction? Those are not interchangeable. A rewrite that helps one may do nothing for the others.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:54:- The Tao screen arrives too early and too weakly. Before the localization protocol is fixed, one cannot tell whether the candidate's supposedly NS-specific feature survives the actual estimate rather than only the bare identity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:64:- The natural test family is too familiar. Lamb-vector, projected form, and vorticity transport are exactly the rewrites one would expect to collapse back to the same structure unless some additional mechanism is injected. The mission context already suggests that at least part of this family has been effectively stress-tested.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:78:- It treats geometry, near-Beltrami structure, and tensor effects as things to subtract away before believing a gain. That is too purity-driven for this mission. The live beyond-De-Giorgi mechanism may be hybrid rather than purely algebraic.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:87:This is the right pressure test, but the chain is too eager to move from a local estimate improvement to a theorem path.
