/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:47:This concern is real but not fatal. The project already knows that the vorticity route hits the same `beta = 4/3` barrier and that Beltrami cancellation is fragile. Retesting those directions is only justified if the refined chain states exactly what new localized estimate, commutator accounting, or Tao-relevant comparison is being added.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:75:This is a fair criticism. Given what is already known about Beltrami fragility, geometry should be part of the first serious evaluation, not a late purity test. The refined chain should specify the perturbation metric early and classify candidate signals as generic, geometry-entangled, or geometry-only.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:94:4. Replace the loose Tao filter with an explicit NS-versus-averaged discriminator.
