/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:125:- It imports a concentration-compactness template without first justifying that Navier-Stokes has the right rigidity ecology for that template to be more than aspirational.
