/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/selected/chain-01.md:50:- Expected output: a candidate table with Tao verdict, prior-art note, and live/dead status.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:7:The problem is that the chain is still organized around the hope that one carefully chosen tensor observable can compress a genuinely nonlocal pressure-coupled mechanism into something coercive. That is the exact point where this literature usually fails. The chain knows the debt exists, but it still treats the existence of a good observable as a live default rather than as the exceptional outcome that must be earned early. So as a falsification program it is strong; as a positive regularity route it still looks overrated.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:15:- The representation package is not the main unresolved choice. The real unresolved choice is the theorem-level endpoint. "Full stretching control," "pressure-Hessian/strain defect control," and "harmonic-moment cancellation" are not three versions of one bottleneck; they are three different proof architectures.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:17:- The local-plus-harmonic pressure split is useful bookkeeping, but the step still risks understating what the harmonic side means. The harmonic contribution is not a perturbative decoration; it is the surviving expression of exterior freedom at the same critical scale as the local term.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:26:- The candidate menu is crowded with familiar descendants of the alignment and restricted-Euler literature: eigenvalue-gap combinations, vorticity-to-eigenframe alignment, pressure/strain misalignment, and defect observables. A table can make these look newly systematized without making them new.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:28:- "Record the exact Tao discriminator" is not operational yet. What exact averaged comparison is being used, and what quantitative feature must fail there? Without that, Tao sensitivity becomes a label attached after the fact to whichever observable seems most NS-flavored.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:38:- The local/harmonic split can be written down explicitly, but explicit splitting is not close to closure. The far-field harmonic data can alter the pressure Hessian without respecting the local geometric picture that made the observable attractive.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:42:The hidden assumption here is strong: that there exists a low-complexity observable whose information survives the passage from local tensor geometry to full harmonic-moment accounting. That is exactly what prior pressure-structure routes have not been able to produce.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:44:### Step 4 - Stress-test Tao sensitivity and packaging robustness
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:49:- The Tao test is still slippery. An averaged quadratic model may destroy a feature for trivial bookkeeping reasons or preserve a feature in a way that says nothing about coercive usefulness. "Not preserved by averaging" is not yet evidence of theorem relevance.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:50:- Many pressure-Hessian identities are NS-specific in algebraic form while still being non-coercive analytically. The step risks conflating exact NS specificity with usable NS specificity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:59:- A proposition-scale target can be cosmetically sharp while hiding the whole problem in the first missing lemma. In this area, the missing lemma is very often exactly the unavailable coercive estimate on the dangerous part of the pressure Hessian.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:74:The central gamble is that a small family of invariant tensor observables can meaningfully constrain the full pressure-Hessian contribution, including harmonic far-field freedom. That is a severe compression step, and the chain does not really justify why it should work beyond hopeful analogy.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:78:This branch lives directly next to existing work on strain-vorticity alignment, eigenvalue geometry, restricted Euler defects, pressure-Hessian modeling, and conditional regularity criteria. Novelty screening belongs before the observable shortlist becomes emotionally favored, not after.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:80:### 4. Tao sensitivity is being asked to do too much conceptual work
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:82:The mission is right to require Tao sensitivity. But "destroyed by averaging" is only a necessary discriminator, not a positive mechanism. A quantity can be genuinely NS-specific and still be analytically powerless. The chain sometimes sounds as if Tao sensitivity itself is a form of leverage.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:86:The negative branch is realistic: one can imagine a sharp memo showing that tensor-pressure structure remains informative yet non-coercive after full nonlocal accounting. The positive branch requires a rare event: a robust, invariant, Tao-sensitive observable that survives harmonic freedom and actually buys a theorem-level gain. The chain does not calibrate those odds honestly enough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:96:What is weak is the underlying bet: that one can distill enough of the pressure-coupled tensor dynamics into a robust observable to gain coercive control. That is precisely the compression that earlier tensor and pressure-structure routes have repeatedly failed to make decisive. The most credible output here is therefore not a proposition-scale regularity mechanism, but a sharper obstruction memo explaining why the pressure-Hessian route remains structurally informative and yet analytically nonclosing once the full nonlocal debt is paid.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/selected/chain-02.md:3:## Central Premise
