/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-01.md:170:is now designed to certify exactly where the pressure-Hessian route stops
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:5:This chain is disciplined about one real danger: accidentally reviving the dead De Giorgi machinery under Lorentz-space language. That is its best feature. Its main weakness is deeper: weak-type or Lorentz structure is a norm package, not an evident Navier-Stokes-specific mechanism. Under the mission's own Tao filter, that is a serious problem from the start, because weak-type Calderon-Zygmund, interpolation, and endpoint singular-integral technology are exactly the sort of harmonic-analysis assets the averaged model is meant to preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:16:- Choosing one endpoint target in advance is methodologically neat and mathematically risky. Weak-type local regularity, distribution-function control, and concentration bounds are not equivalent formulations of one live mechanism; they are different programs with different closure burdens. Freezing one too early invites narrative selection rather than evidence-driven selection.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:27:- The proposed package is dominated by generic harmonic-analysis tools: weak-type Calderon-Zygmund bounds, Lorentz interpolation, endpoint pressure estimates. Under the mission context, that is already presumptively Tao-compatible, not a live source of NS-specific leverage.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:28:- The distinction between "genuinely weak-type" inputs and inputs that immediately upgrade to strong-type is not the decisive split. The more serious split is between inputs that survive localization, truncation, and nonlinear interaction bookkeeping and inputs that do not. Many weak-type estimates are too soft to multiply, localize, or close under pressure decomposition without paying stronger norms elsewhere.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:30:- The pressure part is especially suspect. Endpoint pressure estimates in Lorentz spaces sound differentiated, but pressure localization is exactly where cutoff commutators and decomposition debt tend to force one back into stronger spaces or non-endpoint control.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:31:- Prior-art overlap is not front-loaded enough. The mission context itself names Lorentz-space De Giorgi as an untested lead, but the broader endpoint-criterion literature is already crowded. Without an early novelty screen, Step 2 can rediscover known endpoint statements or known nonclosures and mistake that for branch-specific progress.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:33:Failure mode: Step 2 assembles a respectable ledger of weak-type tools that is either Tao-compatible generic analysis or too brittle to survive the local weak-solution setting.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:39:- "Endpoint regularity criterion," "weak-type concentration inequality," and "localized pressure-transport control statement" are families of outcomes, not engines. None of them explains why weak-type information should propagate, sharpen, or contradict blowup.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:40:- Rejecting disguised level-set recursion is correct but incomplete. A route can avoid level-set iteration and still rely on hidden replacement iteration through covering, epsilon-regularity improvement, repeated truncation, or profile extraction. The chain is screening one disguise while leaving others wide open.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:43:- The pressure-transport option is especially vulnerable to prior failure patterns. Once pressure and localization enter honestly, one is very close to the old burden stack, just stated in endpoint language rather than `U_k` language.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:45:Failure mode: Step 3 promotes a "mechanism" that is either a renamed endpoint criterion with no dynamic engine behind it or a pressure-localization package that quietly recreates the old debt in a new norm.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:47:### Step 4 - Charge localization debt and apply the Tao screen
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:51:- The Tao screen should have bitten in Step 2, not after a candidate mechanism is promoted. If the tool package is already weak-type singular integrals plus interpolation, then the branch is already living inside the generic harmonic-analysis zone unless an exact NS-only feature has been named.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:52:- Localization debt here is not a minor technical audit. It is likely the decisive killer. Weak-type bounds are notoriously fragile under truncation, cutoff insertion, local pressure decomposition, and distribution-function bookkeeping. Treating this as a late screening step understates how central the problem is.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:53:- The `4/3` ceiling is not the only relevant failure signature. A route can avoid reproducing the explicit old ceiling and still be dead because it never leaves Tao-compatible analysis or never closes under localization.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:65:- The negative-output menu is too narrow for the likely reality. The branch may fail simultaneously because there is no distinct weak-type package, no non-iterative mechanism, and no Tao-sensitive leverage. Forcing a single narrow negative can over-clean the actual obstruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:74:This is the core problem. Lorentz and weak-type norms may be useful containers for borderline estimates, but they are not obviously exact-NS features. The mission asks for a property the averaged model destroys. On its face, this chain starts from tools the averaged model should preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:80:### 3. Tao-sensitivity is back-loaded instead of front-loaded
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:82:The planner says Tao's averaged-NS filter is mandatory. This chain does not operationalize that soon enough. It allows a long audit of weak-type packaging before forcing the question whether the package is anything more than preserved harmonic analysis.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:86:In this branch, localization is not a technical afterthought. It is where the weak-type fantasy is most likely to die. If a weak-type estimate does not survive cutoffs, local pressure splitting, and truncation bookkeeping, then it is not a live local regularity mechanism.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:90:The route sits next to endpoint regularity criteria, Lorentz refinements, and weak-space formulations that have been studied for years. Because the chain is framed at the level of architecture rather than a sharply new identity or monotonic quantity, it is especially vulnerable to rediscovering known statements or known reasons they do not close.
