/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:5:The attacker is mostly right. The original chain had a real discriminator: whether exact Navier-Stokes triad geometry contains structure that a Tao-style averaging would wash out. It also had better kill conditions than many speculative Fourier-symbol routes. But it still allowed too much freedom before committing to a proof-relevant bottleneck, and that makes it too easy to generate attractive symbolic memos without earning theorem-level leverage.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:7:The right repair is not to discard the chain. It is to make it bottleneck-first and obstruction-first. A positive branch should survive only if one exact triad feature can be written as an explicit candidate inequality for one fixed estimate and still remain useful after shell summation, mixed-helicity restoration, and any required localization.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:17:### 2. The Tao comparator and the test for "real structure" are under-specified
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:21:The attacker is correct that "Tao-sensitive" can become rhetorical unless the comparison class is fixed precisely. The original chain also did not give a sufficiently invariant test for whether a feature is structural rather than representational. The refined chain keeps the comparator, but only as an operational check relative to a fixed target estimate.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:33:This criticism lands. Same-helicity preference, Beltrami depletion language, and restricted-interaction folklore are well known failure modes in this area. A mechanism that only survives on a thin or already familiar class should not be promoted. The refined chain therefore requires the prior-art comparison and, if a restricted class is used, a quantified statement of how much of the relevant transfer or shell sum that class actually carries.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:39:The original chain knew where the graveyard was, but it treated those items too much like a later stress test. In reality they are the main proof obligations. The refined version makes reconstruction explicit: shell summation, angular multiplicity, mixed-helicity contamination, nonlocal interactions, and localization losses all have to be charged before anything is called live.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:64:2. It demotes the Tao comparator from a rhetorical discriminator to an operational comparison tied to that bottleneck.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:66:4. It converts Step 4 into a full reconstruction bill covering shell summation, multiplicity, mixed-helicity effects, nonlocal interactions, and localization debt.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:5:The attack is mostly correct. The original chain has a real strength: it is disciplined about not reviving the exhausted De Giorgi machine under weak-type or Lorentz language. But the attack correctly identifies that the chain still treats weak-type structure too much like a candidate mechanism rather than a norm package that must earn its way into a genuinely Navier-Stokes-specific contradiction line.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:10:- whether that package survives localization and pressure bookkeeping in the actual local weak-solution setting;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:23:This is a strong criticism. The proposed weak-type package is dominated by Calderon-Zygmund, interpolation, and endpoint singular-integral technology, which is exactly the territory the Tao filter makes suspect. The attack is also right that localization and nonlinear bookkeeping are more decisive than the weak-type versus strong-type distinction by itself, and that prior-art overlap needs to be screened earlier.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:28:The attack is correct that endpoint criteria, concentration inequalities, and pressure-transport statements are outcome families, not mechanisms. A positive branch must name what actual Navier-Stokes-specific feature produces propagation, coercivity, or contradiction, and must screen for broader disguised replacement iterations, not only literal level-set recursion.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:33:The Tao screen and localization debt arrive too late in the original chain. For this branch, those are not downstream refinements. They are architecture-level admission tests. The added failure mode of "no mechanism, only endpoint packaging" is also correct and should be explicit.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:38:The attack is right that a theorem-like conditional statement can conceal circularity if its missing lemma is effectively the full problem, and it is right that the negative output may be genuinely stacked rather than narrowly single-cause. But requiring a theorem-like endpoint claim is still useful once the chain has already enforced mechanism, localization, and Tao screens. The refinement should therefore keep the theorem-like option while allowing stacked obstruction as the default honest negative.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-03.md:43:This is the core critique. Weak-type and Lorentz norms can encode borderline control, but by themselves they are not an exact feature of the Navier-Stokes nonlinearity. Any live positive route must identify what NS-specific ingredient weak-type packaging is carrying.
